com.sap.spe.condmgnt.customizing

Interface IConditionGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface IConditionGroup
extends java.io.Serializable
    ConditionGroup associates a (text string) name with a set of accessible tables and types, and provides methods to determine if specific tables or types are permitted by the condition group.
